                     <script>var container = document.querySelector("#hp-live-band-container");
var band = document.querySelector("#hp-live-band-list");
function debounce(callback, timeout) {
  let timeoutId;
  return function() {
    clearTimeout(timeoutId);
    timeoutId = setTimeout(() => {
      callback();
    }, timeout);
  };
}
function handleLiveBandOverflow() {
  if (band.offsetWidth > container.offsetWidth) {
    container.style.justifyContent = "flex-start";
  } else {
    container.style.justifyContent = "center";
  }
}
;
var debouncedLiveBandFn = debounce(handleLiveBandOverflow, 250);
if (band) {
  window.addEventListener("resize", debouncedLiveBandFn);
  handleLiveBandOverflow();
}</script>

				// NYT apps resize function
				// Resizes the interactive webview height after a 1 second pause
				// Don't run resizer if it's in a programming list webview
				if (window.NYTG && window.NYTG.enqueue && !document.querySelector('#programming-list')) {
					setTimeout(function () {
						var container = document.querySelector('.covid-tracker-wrapper .dashboard');
						var windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
						function resize() {
							var height = container.offsetHeight;
							window.NYTG.enqueue(JSON.stringify({ id: 0, type: 'resize', options: { height: height } }));
						}
						window.addEventListener('resize', function () {
							if (window.innerWidth != windowWidth) {
								windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
								resize();
							}
						});
						resize();
					}, 1000);
				}
			})();
		</script>
